<!--- Guidance for Administrator samplePlan screen --->

<ul>
	<li>Create a fictitious dept. for your Sample Plan, and indicate that in the name: e.g., &ldquo;Dept. of Arctic Studies (fictitious dept.)&rdquo; or &ldquo;Dept. of Arctic Studies (sample plan only)&rdquo;.
	</li>
	<li>To replace your Sample Plan with another, simply upload the new plan; the old plan will be deleted
	</li>
	
	<li>UC Berkeley's Sample Plan is used as the default Sample Plan. Replace it with your own when ready. 
	</li>
	
	<li>Creating your Sample Plan will take a few hours; at any time, you can select the default Sample Plan.</li>
    <li>Whether you are selecting your own Sample Plan or the Default Sample Plan, be sure to hit the &ldquo;Set Sample Plan&rdquo; button.</li>
</ul>

